{
  local d = (import 'doc-util/main.libsonnet'),
  '#':: d.pkg(name='check', url='', help='"Check is the Schema for the Checks API. Synthetic Monitoring checks are tests that run on selected probes at defined intervals and report metrics and logs back to your Grafana Cloud account. The target for checks can be a domain name, a server, or a website, depending on what information you would like to gather about your endpoint. You can define multiple checks for a single endpoint to check different capabilities. Official documentation https://grafana.com/docs/grafana-cloud/testing/synthetic-monitoring/create-checks/checks/"'),
